### 0) Test if backend is running
GET http://localhost:5001/

######################
# PROJECT APIs
######################

### 1) CREATE a new project
POST http://localhost:5001/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mangrove Plantation 6",
  "description": "Planting mangroves to save coastal carbon.",
  "location": "Goa",
  "carbonSaved": 500
}

### 2) GET all projects
GET http://localhost:5001/api/projects

### 3) UPDATE a project (replace <PROJECT_ID> with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:5001/api/projects/68cd8e04132eb1b0954d7681
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Project",
  "location": "Updated Location",
  "carbonSaved": 1000
}

### 4) DELETE a project (replace <PROJECT_ID> with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:5001/api/projects/68cd8e04132eb1b0954d7681

### 5) BONUS – TOTAL PROJECT COUNT
GET http://localhost:5001/api/projects/bonus/count/all

### 6) BONUS – TOTAL CARBON SAVED
GET http://localhost:5001/api/projects/bonus/carbon/total

